OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAsda consults on cutting   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpay for 7,000 workers      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Supermarket chain Asda is considering  
OL,6, whether to cut the pay of 7,000 staff  
OL,7, in the south east of England to bring  
OL,8, it in line with its other stores.      
OL,10,FStaff at 39 stores outside the M25 have
OL,11,Fbeen paid more for decades to offset a 
OL,12,Fhigher cost of living closer to London.
OL,14,FA spokesperson said all Asda staff had 
OL,15,Frecently been given a 10% pay rise to  
OL,16,Fhelp with soaring inflation.           
OL,18,FThe GMB union said Asda was set to fire
OL,19,Fworkers who refused to agree to the new
OL,20,Fconditions.                            
